%p.blue-paragraph From free dictionary: A remedy or other agent used to neutralize or counteract the effects of a poison.

%p Padzahr is a social enterprise. We want to democratise data, giving communities, organisations and individuals a platform from which to make decisions and influence policy.
%p Big data has long been the domain of multinational companies and governments. With all the knowledge comes all the power. Affecting change is a challenge without hard facts to back up arguments. Our aim is to level the playing field.
